***Maximals/Autobots***

: : Rodimus Prime : :

Rodimus pulls Nightlight close. He slowly wipes her tears away before letting his head slump, their foreheads touching.

He now spoke to her in a whisper.

Rodimus Prime: There is still some time, but we shouldn&#39;t put all our egss in one basket. What if the gun fails? I have more faith in the Matrix. If I can find it, i know I can protect us. All of us. Please, let me try to do that. Let me keep you and Elita safe. I love you.

Rodimus tils his head to the right, catching her lips with his, sharing a emotional kiss.

: : Kup : :

Kup had grown tired of sitting around the base. Unicron was coming and he needed to be doing something about it.

Kup transformes to his truck form and heads for the Uber Gun sight. He was going to help, dammit.

***Predacons***

: : SharpClaws/Wolfenstein : :

SharpClaws uses his claws to slice and metal beam in half. he then tosses that half to Wolfenstein, who catches it. Wolf then starts to torch it onto the correct place on the Uber Gun.

Wolfenstein: I just hope we finish this damn thing in time...To save our lives.

***Tripredacus***

: : Tyrael/Darkangel/DeathStar/Dreadplague : :

Tyrael looked to his command team who were all assembled in the war room.

Tyrael: You all have done well in your duties up untill this point. Any commander would be proud to have you. Now we are coming upon the 11th hour. unicron will arrive soon. The weapon must be completed. I&#39;m sending you all to go help with it. Move out!

Darkangel/DeathStar/Dreadplague: Yes, sir! Move out, guys!

The three Tripredacus agents transform to their alternate modes and leave the Tripred base. Moving towards the Uber Gun sight.

OOC: Are the communication jammers still in orbit or were they taken down when I was away?


